			<h3>Summary:</h3><br/>
			<p>"Daily Lives of High School Boys" is an anime series that revolves around the daily lives of three high school boys, Tadakuni, Yoshitake, and Hidenori. This slice-of-life comedy series takes a humorous approach to the everyday experiences of high school boys, from mundane activities like going to class to more adventurous endeavours like going on a school trip.</p>

