            <li>
			<h4>Tadakuni</h4>
			{# <br/><center></center><br/> #}
            <p>The actual main character, but there are a few episodes where Tadakuni isn't even mentioned. The most reserved of the trio, and often serves as the voice of reason. He is also highly introspective and thoughtful.</p><br/>
